\id 1TH NT0013 Tsikimba (kdl) (Auna Kambari) 2010
\h 1 Tasaloniya
\toc1 Ukanikorongi u Kagita̱ Ubana a Asu u Aza a Tasaloniya
\toc2 1 Tasaloniya
\toc3 1 Tas.
\mt2 Ukanikorongi u Kagita̱ Ubana a Asu u
\mt1 Aza a Tasaloniya
\is1 Ukukpa̱ u kadyanshi
\ip An Bulus kotsoi ukorongu ukanikorongi u na vi, aku u korongi kpam u roku ubana a asu u Atoni a Tasaloniya. Tasaloniya ilyuci i ucira iꞌya a ikengi i kushiva̱ n kuden ku pige. Pini a asu vi, atoni a ameli a ɗa pini ushani. Bulus tuwa̱ ta̱ a Tasaloniya u wenishikei ama ukuna u Yesu. U yan ta̱ dem manyan ma uyan atani tsa̱ra̱ u tsa̱ra̱ ikebe. Atoni a ameli ushani a woko ta̱ Atoni a Yesu. Aza a Yahuda a ɗa aꞌa̱ri pini a woko ta̱ dem Atoni.
\ip An a yain aꞌayin, aza ɗa a ka tono n ama a ilyuci yi a gita̱i malyon, pini nala, a lokoi pini Bulus. An nala u wurai, Bulus tuwa̱ ta̱ u suki kaɓa̱ngi ka ne Timoti u tuko yi alabari a Atoni a ɗa aꞌa̱ri a Tasaloniya vi. Timoti tuko yi ta̱ alabari a shinga, an u kotsoi upana alabari a shinga yi ɗa Bulus korongi ukanikorongi vi.
\ip Uwenishike u pige u ɗa wa̱ri pini a ukanikorongi u na vi u ɗa aꞌayin a ɗa Yesu wa doku wa gono pini na a likimba. Ili ushani ya gita̱ ta̱ a aꞌayin a nala yi. Tsa reve kain ka ili yi ya gita̱ wa, adama a nala u gan ta̱ tsu rongo mai tyoku ɗa Kashila̱ ka ciga hal n tsu vani kain ki. Gba̱ ili i na yi Bulus dana ta̱ iꞌya pini a ukanikorongi u na vi.
\is1 Ili iꞌya iꞌa̱ri a tagara̱da u na vi
\io1 Idyani (1:1-3)
\io1 Upityanangu u aza a Tasaloniya n iryoci (1:4–3:13)
\io1 Uma u ɗa wa zuwa Kashila̱ ka pana kayanyan (4:1-12)
\io1 Ili iꞌya tsa fuɗa tsa wene Asheku a gono baci (4:13–5:11)
\io1 Idani i makorishi n idyani (5:12-28)
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 A̱tsu an Bulus n Sila n Timoti a̱tsa tsa korongu ukanikorongi u na ubana a asu u Atoni a Tasaloniya. Ele dem aza a Kashila̱ Tata u tsunu a ɗa kpam aza a Asheku Yesu Kawauwi aza ɗa aꞌa̱ri a asu u nala vi. Ma yan ta̱ kavasu na̱ n foli Kashila̱ ka wenike ukuna u shinga u ne ara ɗe kpam u zuwuka ɗa̱ una̱ u shinga na̱ ndishi n shinga.
\s1 Upityanangu u aza a Tasaloniya
\p 
\v 2 Tsu tsu rongo ta̱ ucikpa Kashila̱ adama a ɗe gba̱. Kpam gba̱ aꞌayin a ɗa baci tsa yan kavasu, tsu tsu ciɓa ɗa̱ ta̱ dem.
\v 3 Aꞌayin a ɗa baci tsa dansa ukuna u ɗe n Kashila̱ Tata u tsunu, tsu tsu dansa ta̱ ukuna u ili iꞌya i tsu yan adama a upityanangu u ɗe, kpam tsu tsu dansa ta̱ manyan ma i tsu yan an ya ciga atoku, tsu tsu dansa ta̱ kpam tyoku ɗa i tsu rongo uzuwa uma a asu u Asheku Yesu Kawauwi aꞌayin a ɗa baci iꞌa̱ri a asuvu a upana u ikyamba.\fig Kavasu|src="1 Thessalonians_1_3.tif" size="span" loc="1Thessalonians 1:3" ref="1 Tas. 1:3"\fig*
\p 
\v 4 Aje a va̱, Kashila̱ ka ciga ɗa̱ ta̱, kpam tsu reve ta̱ u ɗanga̱sa ɗa̱ ta̱ tsa̱ra̱ i woko ama a ne.
\v 5 An tsu tonuko ɗa̱ Kadyanshi ka Shinga, n udyanshi u ɗa koshi wa, shegai n ucira u ɗa. Kulu Keri ka ku zuwa ɗa̱ i reve ili iꞌya tsu danai vi mayun ɗa. Kpam an tsu rongoi n a̱ɗa̱, i wene ta̱ tyoku ɗa tsu rongoi a uwenike ukuna u maci u akani vi.
\v 6 Nala dem, i rongo ta̱ tyoku ɗa tsu rongoi n tyoku ɗa Asheku a rongoi. A asuvu a upana u ikyamba dem, i wusha ta̱ akani yi kpam Kulu Keri ku zuwa ɗa̱ ta̱ i yain maza̱nga̱.
\p 
\v 7 Nala i wokoi iryoci i ama gba̱ aza ɗa a ka tono Asheku a uɓongu u Masidaniya n Akataya.
\v 8 Adama a ɗe, kadyanshi ka Asheku ka kyawan ɗe gba̱ ko nte wa a uɓongu u na vi, hal gba̱m kapala n asu u na vi. Upityanangu u ɗe n Kashila̱ a reve ta̱ n u ɗa ko nte wa. Adama a nala tsa ciga gba̱m tsu yain kadyanshi a kaci ka nala wa.
\v 9 Ama yi n kaci ka le a tsu rongo ta̱ uyan kadyanshi tyoku ɗa i ryabusa tsu. A tsu dansa ta̱ dem tyoku ɗa i kpatala̱kai ameli kucina̱, aku ya gbashika Kashila̱ ka mayun n ka uma.
\v 10 A tsu dansa ta̱ dem tyoku ɗa ya vana Maku ma ne Yesu u tuwa̱ a zuba. Kashila̱ ka ꞌya̱nga̱sa̱ ta̱ Yesu a ukpa̱, gogo‑na kpam Yesu nala vi aya wa wauwa tsu a upana u ikyamba u upan u ne u ɗa wa tuwa̱.
\c 2
\s1 Manyan ma Bulus a Tasaloniya
\p 
\v 1 Ama a va̱, i reve ta̱ gai utuwa̱ u ɗa tsu tuwa̱i tsu kyawan ɗa̱ u gbani u ɗa wa. \x ◊ \xo 2:1 \xt Ask. 17:1-10.\x*
\v 2 I reve ta̱ an tsa̱ri a Filibi kahu tsu tuwa̱ ara ɗe. \x ◊ \xo 2:2 \xt Ask. 16:19-24.\x* Nte a zuwa tsu tsu panai ikyamba pini kpam a yanka tsu tsilai. Shegai Kashila̱ ka tsunu ka na̱ka̱ tsu ta̱ ugbami u asuvu u ɗa tsa tonusuko ɗa̱ Kadyanshi ka Shinga ka ne a kateshe, ko an u wokoi ama ushani pini a ka ka̱ngusu tsu ta̱.
\v 3 Akani a ɗa tsu tuko ɗa̱, aꞌa̱ri n kaɓan wa. Tsu tuko ɗa̱ a ɗa tsa̱ra̱ tsu yain ugboji wa. Ryafa ɗa tsa ciga tsu ryafa ɗa̱ wa. Nala wa̱ri wa, ko kenu!
\v 4 Kashila̱ ka wene tsu ta̱ tsa̱ri mai ɗa gai i zuwai u na̱ka̱ tsu Kadyanshi ka Shinga ka ne tsa̱ra̱ tsu tonusuko aza ɗa a buwai vi. Ili iꞌya tsa ciga iꞌya, tsu zuwa Kashila̱ ka pana kayanyan, kpaci aya uza ɗa u kondoi atakasuvu a tsunu. Tsu tsu zuwuka kadyanshi ka ama atsuvu wa.
\v 5 I reve ta̱ mai tsu tsu cikpala ɗa̱ n kaɓan wa, kpam Kashila̱ n kaci ka ne wa wenishike ta̱ ili iꞌya tsu yain adama a kurura a ɗa wa.
\v 6 Tsu tsu yan ili adama a ɗa tsa tsa̱ra̱ tsupige ara ɗe, ko ara uza wa.
\p Kpaci a̱tsu asuki a Kawauwi a ɗa, tsa fuɗa ta̱ tsa yanka ucira u nala manyan tsu zuwa ɗa̱ i na̱ka̱ tsu ili iꞌya tsa ciga.
\v 7 Shegai tsu yan nala wa, aku tsu vakunki kaci utuwa̱ ara ɗe tyoku ɗa mma u tsu comuko kpam u kirana na̱ mmuku n ne.
\v 8 Tsu ciga ɗa̱ ta̱ cika kpam tsu pana ta̱ kayanyan tsu tuko ɗa̱ Kadyanshi ka Shinga ka Kashila̱, kpam dem tsu pana ta̱ kayanyan tsu ɓa̱nga̱ ɗa̱ a ili dem, kpaci i woko ɗe aza ɗa tsa ciga cika.
\p 
\v 9 Ama a va̱, i ciɓa ta̱ tyoku ɗa tsu yain manyan cika an tsa̱ri kaɓolo n a̱ɗa̱. Kaara n kayin tsu tsu moɗono ta̱ tsu tsa̱ra̱ ikebe tsa̱ra̱ ili iꞌya baci dem tsa ciga tsu tsila i woko ili kadambula ara uza wa, aꞌayin a ɗa tsa̱ri pini n tsu yanyi kuɓari ku Kadyanshi ka Shinga ka Kashila̱.
\v 10 Eɗa ama a tsunu aza ɗa i wenei ukuna vi n aꞌeshi a ɗe, nala dem Kashila̱, a̱tsu tsa̱ ta̱ sarara n ukuna u mayun, ko uza wa na̱ka̱ tsu unyushi tyoku ɗa tsu yanka ɗa̱ wa, eɗa aza ɗa i wushuki n Asheku.
\v 11 Kpam i reve ta̱ tsu tono ta̱ n a̱ɗa̱ mai tyoku ɗa tata u tsu tono na̱ mmuku n ne.
\v 12 Tsu folo ɗa̱ ta̱, kpam tsu gbamatangu ɗa̱ ta̱. Tsu zuwa ta̱ ya dem u rongo ure u ɗa wa na̱ka̱ Kashila̱ tsupige, kpaci u isa̱ ɗa̱ ta̱ i uwa a tsugono tsu ne i tsa̱ra̱ kaɓon a tsupige tsu ne.
\p 
\v 13 Kain dem tsu tsu cikpa ta̱ Kashila̱ an i wushuki n akani a ɗa tsu tuko ɗa̱. I danai idani i tsunu i ama iꞌya koshi wa. I wushai akani yi dere tyoku ɗa aꞌa̱ri mayun: Akani a Kashila̱ a ɗa. Kpam akani a nala yi a ka rongo ta̱ uyan manyan ara ɗe aza ɗa i wushuki.
\p 
\v 14 Ama a va̱, an i wushuki n ili iꞌya tsu danai, ama a ɗe a foro ɗa̱ ta̱. Nala i wokoi tyoku u Atoni a Kashila̱ a ɗa aꞌa̱ri a Yahuda. Ama a nala yi a wushuku ta̱ n Yesu Kawauwi, aku ama a le aza a Yahuda a foro le dem.
\v 15 Aza a Yahuda a nala yi a wuna ta̱ ntsumate n le, hal aza roku a le gba̱m a wunai Yesu Asheku. Gogo‑na a zuwa tsu ta̱ tsu panai ikyamba kpam a loko tsu. Ama a nala yi a yan ili iꞌya Kashila̱ ka pana kayanyan wa, kpam a ɓishinkai gba̱ ama uwusha ukuna u shinga,
\v 16 kpaci a ɓishinka tsu ta̱ tsu dansa n Awulawa tsa̱ra̱ kotsu a tsa̱ra̱ iwauwi wa. Nala a rongoi uyansa n a dokusi unyushi u cingi u le. Aku Kashila̱ ka tuwa̱i ka yain upan, u yan le mavura.
\s1 Bulus wa ciga u doku u kyawan le
\p 
\v 17 Ama a va̱, an a loko tsu ara ɗe, tsu ɓa̱ra̱kpa̱ wa, she na tsu ma̱tsa̱i cika tsu gono. Tsu a̱sa̱ka̱ uciɓusa n a̱ɗa̱ wa, ko kenu, kpam tsu ciga ta̱ tsu wene ɗa̱ cika.
\v 18 Mayun ɗa tsa ciga ɗa̱ uwene. Mpa Bulus, n ma̱tsa̱ ta̱ aꞌayin ushani tsa̱ra̱ n tuwa̱ ara ɗe, shegai Kanangasi\f + \fr 2:18 \ft Kanangasi; wata, “Shetan” kala ka dem ka Kala̱pa̱nsi.\f* ka ka̱ngu mu ta̱.
\v 19 Ili iꞌya i zuwai ma ciga n wene ɗa̱ iꞌya, i tuko tsu ta̱ uzuwa u uma, i na̱ka̱ tsu kpam maza̱nga̱, kpam eɗa funi u utsa̱ra̱ u kaci u tsunu. Ya zuwa tsu ta̱ tsu yain maza̱nga̱ a kapala ka Yesu Asheku aꞌayin a ɗa baci u tuwa̱i.
\v 20 Eɗa tsupige tsu tsunu, eɗa kpam maza̱nga̱ ma tsunu.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Adama a nala, an tsu kpa̱ɗa̱i akawunki a upana alabari a ɗe, aku tsu wushuki tsu da a̱tsu tsa shamgba ta̱ a Atina,
\v 2 aku tsu suki Timoti ubana ara ɗe. U yan ta̱ manyan n a̱tsu tyoku u kagbashi ka Kashila̱, kpam u yain kuɓari ku Kadyanshi ka Shinga ka Kawauwi. Tsu suku yi ta̱ tsa̱ra̱ u zuwa ɗa̱ i yain ugbami kpam u gbamatangu upityanangu u ɗe.
\v 3 Tsa ciga i dambula adama a upana u ikyamba u ɗa wa tuwusa̱ ɗa̱ wa. I reve ta̱ gai an upana u ikyamba vi wa tuwa̱, cinda Kashila̱ ka ka ɗanga̱sa tsu.
\p 
\v 4 Aꞌayin a ɗa tsa̱ri n a̱ɗa̱ vi, tsu tsu ronuso ɗa̱ ta̱ atsuvu tsu da upana u ikyamba wa tuwa̱ tsu ta̱ gba̱ tsunu gogo. Kpam i reve ta̱ mai upana u ikyamba u tuwa̱ ɗe.
\v 5 N pana ta̱ alabari a upana u ikyamba u ɗe hal n kpa̱ɗa̱i ukawunku n alabari a ɗa n panai, ɗa i zuwai n suki Timoti vi. N suku yi ta̱ tsa̱ra̱ u wene ko upityanangu u ɗe u buwa pini n ugbami. Ma̱ri n pana ta̱ uwonvo ma wundya ko Uza u Ukondo u fuɗa ɗa̱ ɗe, manyan ma tsunu kpam gba̱ ma woko ma gbani.
\s1 Timoti danai ili iꞌya u wenei
\p 
\v 6 Gogo‑na ɗa Timoti gonoi a asu u nwalu n ne utuwa̱ ara tsunu an u wuta̱i ara ɗe. U tuko tsu ta̱ alabari a shinga a ukuna u upityanangu u ɗe n ukuna u uciga u ɗe. U tonuko tsu ta̱ kpam an iꞌa̱ri tsu a uciɓusa n maza̱nga̱ kpam ya ciga tsu uwene, tyoku ɗa a̱tsu dem tsa ciga ɗa̱ uwene.
\p 
\v 7 Ama a va̱, a̱tsu n kaci ka tsunu dem tsa̱ ta̱ n upana u ikyamba kpam a ka yan tsu mavura cika, shegai tsa̱ ta̱ na̱ nvain n katakasuvu an i shamgbai n ucira a upityanangu u ɗe.
\v 8 Gogo‑na tsu reve ta̱ an iꞌa̱ri kushani n ucira n Asheku, nala vi u doku ta̱ u gbamatangu tsu.
\v 9 Tsu cikpa ta̱ Kashila̱ adama a ɗe cika! Adama a ɗe tsa̱ ta̱ n maza̱nga̱ ma pige a kapala ka Kashila̱.
\v 10 Kaara n kayin tsu tsu yan ta̱ kavasu cika adama a ɗe. Kpam tsu folo ta̱ Kashila̱ ka a̱sa̱ka̱ tsu tsu doku tsu wene ɗa̱, tsa̱ra̱ tsu shaɗangusu ili iꞌya i gusa̱i a asuvu a upityanangu u ɗe.
\p 
\v 11 Kavasu ka tsunu ka Kashila̱ Tata u tsunu n Yesu Asheku a a̱sa̱ka̱ tsu tsu kondo ɗa̱.
\v 12 Tsa ciga ta̱ Asheku a zuwa uciga u ɗe u gbonguro cika hal n i cigamgbani kpam i cigi gba̱ ama, tyoku ɗa dem a̱tsu tsa ciga ɗa̱ cika.
\v 13 Aꞌayin a ɗa baci Asheku a tsunu a ka gono n aza a uwulukpi a ne. Tsu yan ta̱ kavasu u zuwa atakasuvu a ɗe a rongo n ucira cika, tsa̱ra̱ kain ka ugono ka ne i woko uwulukpi a kapala ka Kashila̱ Tata u tsunu kpam ko uza wa takpa ɗa̱ n ukuna u roku wa.
\c 4
\s1 Rongoi mai a kapala ka Kashila̱
\p 
\v 1 A makorishi ama a va̱, tsa folo ɗa̱ ta̱ adama a kala ka Yesu Asheku i rongo a ure u ɗa Kashila̱ ka pana kayanyan. Tsu wenishike ɗa̱ ɗe nala vi kpam hal n gogo‑na nala iꞌa̱ri uyansa. Tsu gbamatangu ɗa̱ ta̱ i lyai kapala n uyansa nala
\v 2 kpaci i ciɓa ta̱ ili iꞌya tsu wenishike ɗa̱ a asuvu a kala ka Yesu Asheku.
\p 
\v 3 Tsa ciga ɗa̱ ta̱ i rongo uwulukpi, kotsu i suma unyushi u cingi u tsishankala.
\v 4 Ya dem u fuɗa u guɓi ikyamba i ne i rongo ure u ɗa wa̱ri uwulukpi n u ɗa kpam ama a ka na̱ka̱ karinga̱.
\v 5 Kotsu i woko agbashi a uciga u atakasuvu a ɗe tyoku ɗa Awulawa a tsu yan wa, kpaci a reve Kashila̱ n ire i ne wa.
\p 
\v 6 Kotsu vu ryafa utoku u vunu Katoni vu bidya uka u ne wa, kpaci Asheku a ka foro ta̱ gba̱ aza a icun i unyushi i cingi i nala yi. Tsu rono ɗa̱ ta̱ atsuvu caupa.
\v 7 Kashila̱ ka isa̱ tsu ta̱ tsu woko uwulukpi, u isa̱ tsu tsa̱ra̱ tsu rongo uma u ɗa wa̱ri n ashinda̱ wa.
\v 8 Gba̱ uza ɗa baci u kpa̱ɗa̱i utono ukuna u na vi, ukuna u vuma ɗa u kpa̱ɗa̱i una̱ka̱ karinga̱ wa, shegai Kashila̱ ka wa̱ri uꞌyuwan, uza ɗa u na̱ka̱ ɗa̱ Kulu Keri ku ne.
\p 
\v 9 Kashila̱ n kaci ka ne u wenishike ɗa̱ ta̱ i cigi atoku a ɗe, adama a nala ili iꞌa̱ la ya zuwa mu n koronku ɗa̱ ukuna u uciga u Atoni u ɗa ya wenike asu u ama a Kashila̱ wa.
\v 10 Mayun ɗa, ko gogo‑na iꞌa̱ ta̱ n uciga ushani ubana a asu u Atoni a ɗa aꞌa̱ri a uyamba u Masidaniya. Ama a va̱, ko an u wokoi nala, tsu folo ɗa̱ ta̱ i doku i cigi le cika.
\p 
\v 11 Ili iꞌya ya ciga cika iꞌya: i rongo n uma u ɗe shiriri, yawunsai a ukuna u manyan ma ɗe koshi, kpam i yain manyan n akere a ɗe, tyoku ɗa tsu tonuko ɗa̱ caupa.
\v 12 Adama a nala, ama ɗa bawu aꞌa̱ri Atoni a ka na̱ka̱ ɗa̱ ta̱ karinga̱ adama a uma u ɗa ya rongo, kpam ya zuwa ucira u ɗe a asu u ama a na̱ka̱ ɗa̱ ikebe wa.
\s1 Tyoku ɗa Asheku a ka gono
\p 
\v 13 Ama a va̱, ma ciga ta̱ i reve ili iꞌya ya gita̱ n Atoni a ɗa a kuwa̱i. Kotsu i shaɗangu n unamgbukatsuma̱ adama a le tyoku u ama ɗa bawu aꞌa̱ri n uzuwa u uma wa.
\v 14 Tsu wushuku ta̱ Yesu kuwa̱ ta̱ kpam u ꞌya̱nga̱i n uma. Kpam dem tsu wushuku ta̱ Kashila̱ ka gonuko baci Yesu, wa gonuko yi ta̱ kaɓolo n ama ɗa a pityanangi n eyi kahu a kuwa̱.
\p 
\v 15 Yesu Asheku u tonuko tsu ta̱ u gono baci, a̱tsu aza ɗa tsa̱ri n uma aꞌayin a ɗa Asheku a ka gono vi, tsa uwa a kapala ka aza ɗa a lasa tsu wa.
\v 16 Asheku n kaci ka ne wa cipa̱ ta̱ a zuba. Aꞌayin a nala yi ama a ka pana ta̱ kala̱ga̱tsu ka Asheku, kpam a ka pana ta̱ isali i pige a asu u uzapige u atsumate a zuba, a ka pana̱ka le ta̱ a fula̱ kavana ka Kashila̱. Nala gita̱ baci, aku aza ɗa a kuwa̱i a asuvu a Kawauwi a gita̱ a ꞌya̱nga̱.\fig Utuwa̱ u Asheku a zuba u alishi|src="1 Thessalonians_4_16.tif" size="span" loc="1Thessalonians 4:16" ref="1 Tas. 4:16–5:8"\fig*
\v 17 A̱tsu aza ɗa tsa̱ri n uma a likimba, a ka canga tsu ta̱ a asuvu a alishi tsu gawunsa n Asheku a zuba, kpam tsu rongo n eyi ɗe maco.
\v 18 Nala ya gbamatangu atoku n kadyanshi ka nala ki.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 Ama a va̱, ili iꞌa̱ la ya zuwa mu n koronku ɗa̱ ko niɗa ko nwere ɗa ikuna i na yi ya gita̱ wa,
\v 2 kpaci i reve ta̱ mai kain ka Asheku a ka tuwa̱ wa woko ta̱ tyoku ɗa kaboki ka tsu tuwa̱ n kayin.
\v 3 Aꞌayin yi, ama a ka dana ta̱, “Tsa̱ ta̱ na̱ ndishi n shinga kpam tsa̱ n ukuna wa,” kute‑kute aku upana u ikyamba u rukpa̱ le, tyoku ɗa uka u katsuma̱ u tsu pana mɓa̱la̱ ilimaci ya rawa yi baci. Asu wa̱ la u ɗa ama a ka la a upana u ikyamba u nala vi wa.
\p 
\v 4 Ama a va̱, iꞌa̱ri a asuvu a karimbi a ikuna i na yi wa, kpam kotsu i yain majiyan ma kain ka baci kain ka Asheku ka tuwa̱ ɗa̱ tyoku u kaboki wa.
\v 5 Kpaci eɗa̱ mmuku n katyashi n ɗa kpam aza kaara. A̱tsu aza a karimbi n kayin a ɗa wa.
\v 6 Adama a nala she i wundi mai, kotsu i lavuta tyoku u aza ɗa a buwai wa. Shegai i rongo n uma kpam n uka̱na̱ u kaci.
\v 7 N kayin ka a tsu lavuta, aza ɗa kpam a tsu so n kayin ka a tsu so hal a tamgbala̱ka.
\v 8 Shegai a̱tsu aza ɗa tsa̱ri a asuvu a katyashi u gan ta̱ tsu ka̱na̱ kaci ka tsunu. Aꞌayin a ɗa baci Kala̱pa̱nsi ka shila̱ka̱na̱ n a̱tsu, tsu lyai kapala n upityanangu n Yesu n uciga u ama, tyoku ɗa kasoje ka tsu uka mara̱ga̱ a makamba. Tsu zuwa uma u ɗa Yesu wa wauwa tsu, tyoku ɗa kasoje ka tsu uka makun ma kuvon.
\v 9 Tsu yain ili i nala yi kpaci Kashila̱ ka bidya ta̱ ka wauwa tsu a akere a Yesu Kawauwi Asheku. U bidiga kaci ka ne u tsungu upan u ne ara tsunu wa.
\v 10 Ko a̱tsu n uma ko a asuvu a ukpa̱ aꞌayin a ɗa baci u gonoi tsa rongo ta̱ n eyi bawu utyoku, kpaci Yesu Asheku u kuwa̱ ta̱ adama a tsunu.
\v 11 Adama a nala, kotsu i gbamatangu atakasuvu a atoku a ɗe, i rongo a una̱ka̱sa̱ atoku a ɗe adooki, dere tyoku ɗa iꞌa̱ri uyansa.
\s1 Uwenishike u makorishi
\p 
\v 12 Ama a va̱, na̱ka̱i azapige a ɗe tsupige aza ɗa aꞌa̱ri a asuvu a manyan ma Asheku. A yan ta̱ manyan cika a asuvu a ɗe, kpam a tonuko ɗa̱ ta̱ ili iꞌya bawu i gain i yain.
\v 13 Na̱ka̱i ama a na yi karinga̱ cika kpam i cigi le cika adama a manyan ma le. I rongo kpam na̱ ndishi mai n atoku.
\p 
\v 14 Ama a va̱, u ka̱na̱ ta̱ i roni atsuvu a awonvoli. Gbamatangi aza a uwonvo. I ɓa̱nga̱ aza ɗa bawu aꞌa̱ri n ucira, ya dem yanyi ahankuri n eyi.
\p 
\v 15 I kirana kotsu a tsupa ukuna u cingi n ukuna u cingi wa, shegai aꞌayin dem i ma̱tsa̱ i yain ili i shinga a asu u atoku a ɗe n ama gba̱.
\p 
\v 16 Kain dem i yain maza̱nga̱.
\v 17 Rongoi uyan kavasu bawu ubula̱.
\v 18 Ko ndya baci i gita̱i i cikpa Kashila̱, kpaci tyoku ɗa Kashila̱ ka ciga u ɗa la vi, kpam eɗa̱ ama a Yesu Kawauwi a ɗa.
\p 
\v 19 Kotsu i ka̱ngu Kulu Keri wa.
\v 20 Kotsu i goro kadyanshi ka Kashila̱ ka ka wutusa̱ a una̱ u Atoni wa,
\v 21 shegai i kondo ili iꞌya a danai gba̱. Shamkpai ili iꞌya iꞌa̱ri i shinga.
\v 22 Sumai gba̱ ili iꞌya iꞌa̱ri i cingi.
\p 
\v 23 Tsu reve ta̱ Kashila̱ aya uza ɗa u tsu na̱ka̱ ndishi n shinga. Kavasu ka va̱ ka u wulukpe ɗa̱ a ili dem. A̱sa̱ka̱ u ɓishinka kulu ku ɗe, n uma u ɗe, n ikyamba i ɗe uyan u unyushi u cingi ko a ure u eni u ɗa baci, hal Yesu Kawauwi Asheku u gono.
\v 24 Uza ɗa u ɗanga̱sa ɗa̱ u rawa ta̱ i wushuku n eyi, kpam wa yan ta̱ nala.
\p 
\v 25 Ama a va̱, yanka tsu kavasu.
\p 
\v 26 Dana̱sai Atoni n uwambatsa u uwulukpi.
\p 
\v 27 N tonuko ɗa̱ ta̱ a asuvu a ucira u Asheku i yanka gba̱ Atoni ka̱neshi u ukanikorongi u na vi.
\p 
\v 28 Ma ciga ta̱ Asheku a wenike ukuna u shinga u ne a asu u ɗe gba̱. 
